import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, NavLink, Switch, Redirect } from 'react-router-dom'

export default function access(allowed) {
    if (allowed) {
        return (
            <Switch>
                <Route path="/">
                </Route>
                <Route path="/">
                </Route>
                <Route path="/">
                </Route>
                <Redirect to="/"/>
            </Switch>
        )
    }
    return (
        <Switch>
            <Route path="/">
            </Route>
            <Route path="/">
            </Route>
            <Route path="/">
            </Route>
            <Redirect to="/"/>
        </Switch>
    )
}
